result.name: Cute Soft Green Theme - Roblox
result.description: This is the fixed version of the original, now the background works. All credits go to >Alleys< for the colour choices and the artwork which is an original creation by them. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
result.notes: This is the Alt of DittoDino.Disclaimers: Tablets, iPads & phones won't work. Cʜʀᴏᴍᴇ & Oᴘᴇʀᴀ ᴀʀᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏɴʟʏ ʙʀᴏᴡsᴇʀs ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴡᴏʀᴋ ᴡᴇʟʟ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇxᴛᴇɴsɪᴏɴ. Press 'Read more' for further help.
